Look striking and stand out in this gorgeous suit. It features bold embroidery and applique work on the yoke and hem with diamante and sequins for embellishment. This set also has a matching material for churidar and a dupatta with contrasting border and applique work. Wear it with red lips strappy heels and a crystal studded clutch to create a look that invokes envy. * Top: 2.25m * Bottom: 2.25m * Dupatta: 2.0m
